text: Karin Rahamim (; born 23 June 1989) is an Israeli footballer who plays as a forward and has appeared for the Israel women's national team. ==Career== Rahamim has been capped for the Israel national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Israeli women's footballers Category:Israel women's international footballers Category:Women's association football forwards
